---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DynamicPageBlocks from '../components/DynamicPageBlocks.astro';
import { getZeffyDonationUrl } from '../config/siteLinks';

const zeffyDonateUrl = getZeffyDonationUrl();
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Surf Del Mar"
	description="Celebrating the sport and the culture. Preserving the stories and the spirit. Del Mar Historical Society Surfing Festival."
	pageKey="home"
>
	<!-- Hero: full-screen with sunset/surfer background -->
	<section class="hero-long" aria-label="Surf Del Mar Festival">
		<img
			src="/surfdelmar.png"
			alt=""
			class="hero-long-bg"
			width="1200"
			height="800"
			fetchpriority="high"
			data-original-src="/surfdelmar.png"
			onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src=this.getAttribute('data-original-src')||'/surfdelmar.png';"
		/>
		<div class="hero-long-overlay"></div>
		<div class="hero-long-content">
			<h1 class="hero-long-title" data-editable="home.hero.title">Surf Del Mar</h1>
			<p class="hero-long-subtitle" data-editable="home.hero.subtitle">FESTIVAL</p>
			<div class="hero-long-divider"></div>
			<p class="hero-long-tagline" data-editable="home.hero.tagline1">Celebrating the Sport and the Culture</p>
			<p class="hero-long-tagline" data-editable="home.hero.tagline2">Preserving the Stories and the Spirit</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Reunion: two-column -->
	<section class="reunion-section">
		<div class="reunion-container">
			<div class="reunion-col reunion-col-image">
				<div class="reunion-poster-wrap">
					<img src="/Poster.webp" alt="Surf Del Mar Festival poster by John Van Hamersveld" class="reunion-poster" width="600" height="900" />
					<a href="https://www.post-future.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="reunion-poster-btn">See more of John Van Hamersveld's work.</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="reunion-col reunion-col-text">
				<p class="reunion-body" data-editable="home.reunion.body">
					SURF DEL MAR is more than a festival—it's a Reunion, decades in the making. It brings together generations of surfers, storytellers, artists, musicians, authors and filmmakers for a one-of-a-kind event celebrating the sport, the culture, the legacy and the surfing history of Del Mar and the surrounding communities.
				</p>
				<p class="reunion-join" data-editable="home.reunion.join">JOIN US OVER FOUR UNFORGETTABLE DAYS</p>
				<div class="calendar-callout">
					<p class="calendar-callout-dates" data-editable="home.reunion.dates">October 8–11, 2026 – Del Mar, California</p>
				</div>
				<p class="reunion-tagline" data-editable="home.reunion.tagline">Come Be A Part Of The History and The Fun When Surfers Come Together Again</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Don Hansen Tribute -->
	<section class="hansen-section">
		<div class="hansen-container">
			<h2 class="hansen-heading">A Tribute to Don Hansen</h2>

			<div class="hansen-content">
				<div class="hansen-photo-frame">
					<img src="/hanson.png" alt="Don Hansen" class="hansen-photo" width="942" height="910" />
					<span class="photo-caption">Don Hansen (1936–2026)</span>
				</div>

				<p class="hansen-body"><strong>Donald Hansen</strong>, an entrepreneur, athlete and adventurer whose life stretched far beyond any one calling, passed away on March 28th, 2026 at the age of 89.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">To write about Don Hansen is to write about motion: prairie wind, Pacific swell, open sky, mountain trails and the forward pull of a man who never stopped testing the edges of life. Don leaves behind a legacy rooted not only in adventure, but in kindness, mentorship and family.</p>

				<blockquote class="hansen-pullquote">
					"Don moved through life with faith and gratitude, believing in people before they fully believed in themselves."
				</blockquote>

				<p class="hansen-body">Born in 1936 in Aberdeen, South Dakota, Don was raised in Redfield where he spent his youth hunting and fishing before dreaming of California. In 1960, Don founded <strong>Hansen Surfboards</strong> near Cardiff Reef in Encinitas. The shop became a pillar of California surf culture—a gathering place where Don was the heart, mentoring generations of surfers and earning the respect of the global surfing world.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">Don chased challenge everywhere. He surfed big Hawaiian waves when that frontier was still young. In those Pacific swells, Don found his <em>Kulia</em> (koo-lee-ah), stepping into something bigger and pushing past comfort.</p>

				<p class="hansen-body">That appetite for challenge carried him into the open sky as captain of the Airfreight skydiving team, winning national titles and setting world records. Later, on Montana trails, Don "let her buck"—bringing that same spirit to the mountains while taking up team roping with enthusiasm and grit.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<DynamicPageBlocks pageKey="home" />

	<!-- Support / donate (Zeffy); copy editable when logged in as admin -->
	<section class="support-section" aria-labelledby="support-heading">
		<div class="support-inner">
			<h2 id="support-heading" class="support-heading" data-editable="home.support.heading">Support Surf Del Mar</h2>
			<p class="support-text" data-editable="home.support.body">
				Help us keep this festival and our coastal heritage programs going. Donations are processed securely through Zeffy.
			</p>
			<a
				href={zeffyDonateUrl}
				class="btn-support"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
			>
				Donate with Zeffy
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Final CTA -->
	<section class="cta-section">
		<a href="/schedule/" class="btn-schedule">VIEW FULL EVENT SCHEDULE</a>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	/* --- Coastal Vintage palette (use vars where existing) --- */
	.hero-long {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 80vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background-color: var(--color-ink);
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-long-bg {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center center;
		filter: brightness(1.12);
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.hero-long-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(30,46,46,0.6) 0%, rgba(30,46,46,0.25) 50%, transparent 100%);
		z-index: 1;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.hero-long-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		max-width: 720px;
		padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-long-title {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 5.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
		line-height: 1.05;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
	}

	.hero-long-subtitle {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7.5vw, 4.25rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.45em;
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
		opacity: 0.95;
		text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	.hero-long-divider {
		width: 120px;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(229,240,242,0.9), transparent);
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;
	}

	.hero-long-tagline {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.5vw, 2.25rem);
		font-weight: 500;
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem 0;
		opacity: 0.95;
		text-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	/* --- Reunion two-column --- */
	.reunion-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-cream) 0%, var(--color-sand) 50%, var(--color-foam) 100%);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.reunion-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.reunion-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		.reunion-col-image {
			order: 1;
		}
		.reunion-col-text {
			order: 2;
		}
	}

	.reunion-poster-wrap {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.25rem;
	}

	.reunion-poster-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		background: var(--color-ink);
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
	}

	.reunion-poster-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.reunion-poster {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 420px;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
		border-radius: 6px;
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.18), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
		transform: rotate(-2deg);
		transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
	}

	.reunion-poster-wrap:hover .reunion-poster {
		transform: rotate(0deg);
		box-shadow: 0 24px 56px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}

	.reunion-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.35rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.reunion-body {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		line-height: 1.75;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		max-width: 48ch;
	}

	.reunion-join {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}

	.reunion-tagline {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		line-height: 1.45;
		margin: 1.25rem 0 0 0;
		max-width: 42ch;
	}

	.calendar-callout {
		background: rgba(204,228,232,0.75);
		border-left: 4px solid #c9a227;
		padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
	}

	.calendar-callout-label {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem 0;
	}

	.calendar-callout-dates {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.35;
	}

	/* --- Don Hansen Tribute: Editorial Style --- */
	.hansen-section {
		background: var(--color-cream);
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}

	.hansen-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.hansen-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.hansen-heading::after {
		content: '';
		display: block;
		width: 60px;
		height: 3px;
		background: #c9a227;
		margin: 1rem auto 0;
	}

	.hansen-content {
		display: block;
	}

	.hansen-content::after {
		content: '';
		display: table;
		clear: both;
	}

	.hansen-photo-frame {
		float: left;
		width: 40%;
		margin: 0 3rem 2rem 0;
	}

	.hansen-photo {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 4px;
		box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px var(--color-sand);
		border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}

	.photo-caption {
		display: block;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
	}

	.hansen-body {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hansen-pullquote {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
		border-left: 4px solid #c9a227;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		margin: 3rem 0;
		line-height: 1.4;
		clear: right;
	}

	/* --- Support / donate --- */
	.support-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-sand) 0%, var(--color-cream) 100%);
		padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(26, 46, 46, 0.08);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26, 46, 46, 0.06);
	}

	.support-inner {
		max-width: 560px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.support-heading {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.support-text {
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		line-height: 1.65;
		color: var(--color-sepia);
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.btn-support {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.95rem 2rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--color-ink);
		background: var(--color-cream);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-sand-dark);
		border-radius: 50px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(30, 122, 122, 0.2);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, background 0.2s ease;
	}

	.btn-support:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(30, 122, 122, 0.28);
	}

	/* --- Final CTA --- */
	.cta-section {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-foam) 0%, var(--color-sand) 100%);
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.btn-schedule {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.25rem;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--color-cream);
		background: var(--color-sand-dark);
		border-radius: 50px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,122,122,0.35);
		transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
	}

	.btn-schedule:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(30,122,122,0.45);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero-long {
			min-height: 60vh;
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.hero-long-title {
			font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 10vw, 3.5rem);
		}
		.hero-long-subtitle {
			font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 3vw, 1rem);
		}
		.hero-long-tagline {
			font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 2.5vw, 1.1rem);
		}
		.reunion-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.reunion-container {
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
		.reunion-body {
			font-size: 1rem;
			max-width: none;
		}
		.reunion-tagline {
			font-size: 1rem;
			max-width: none;
		}
		.reunion-poster {
			max-width: 100%;
		}
		.reunion-poster-btn {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.25rem;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout {
			padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout-dates {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
		.hansen-section {
			padding: 4rem 1rem;
		}
		.hansen-photo-frame {
			float: none;
			width: 100%;
			margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
			text-align: center;
		}
		.hansen-photo {
			max-width: 300px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px var(--color-sand);
		}
		.hansen-heading {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
		.hansen-pullquote {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			margin: 2rem 0;
		}
		.support-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.support-text {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
		.btn-support {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem;
			font-size: 0.88rem;
		}
		.cta-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		}
		.btn-schedule {
			min-height: 48px;
			padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.reunion-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.25rem;
		}
		.reunion-section {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.hansen-section {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
		}
		.support-section,
		.cta-section {
			padding: 2rem 1rem;
		}
		.calendar-callout-dates {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
